ThingDef.label: Corned beef
ThingDef.description: Salted meat. The shelf life has been significantly extended.

ThingDef.label: Meat
ThingDef.description: Edible animal meat. Rich in protein and fat.

ThingDef.label: Humanoid flesh
ThingDef.description: Humanoid meat. Very few will agree to eat this.

ThingDef.label: Insect meat
ThingDef.description: Large insect meat. It has a large number of veins and glands with fluids. Tastes bad.

ThingDef.label: Plant-based meat
ThingDef.description: Meat based on plant proteins. A dubious replacement for meat for those who cannot eat it for various reasons.

ThingDef.label: Sausages
ThingDef.description: Quite nutritious sausages made from meat and some additives.

ThingDef.label: Meat extract
ThingDef.description: Nourishing meat extract and insect jelly. Does not disgust consumers.
